{"tid":1755272,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一沉百踩！呢個係我地一舉打低敵人既好機會！","createTime":"2019-11-25T13:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T19:27:18.000Z","uid":282006,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f307bef42233db2bb45ca25a91750ad2683211","tid":1755272,"uid":282006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"首先自派膠，我喺選舉前的確係覺得完全唔樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家我見到既係將藍絲廢老保皇popo呢班<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">少數派曱甴</span></span><br />\n消滅既好機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地而家可以盡情引戰，首先以救poly手足開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論班曱甴講乜春都好，最緊要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">獅子開大口</span>，如果手足仲想/可以留守既，要高調地將popo打成為失敗份子，無民意，阻路，錯判總之扣上一切帽子<br />\n<br />\n藍絲喺選舉前最鐘意打飛機就係民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家我地既文宣就可以狂轟濫炸對面，要佢地發開口夢都要記住自己係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">少數派，曱甴</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺對手曾經最得意既地方落手，傷口灑鹽<br />\n帶黎既效果好過落手獅鳥佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然選區議會，最緊要係服務社區，鞏固好呢個手足犧牲換番黎既立足點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地未贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比敵人有任何翻身既機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">It shall be the end of the beginning</span>"},{"pid":"d298e0a231125cca75cf3a560e728cfafaef5942","tid":1755272,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:40:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adc52a6dc7f920bc240eff704b2a4e58378783b","tid":1755272,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"62ef7afaf5cf09c3425aea8ea69aecdd0025b8ec","tid":1755272,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"泛民本土成建制派<br />\n保皇成少數反對派"},{"pid":"ce5729ec54aeb749361841ba5f2476200a575a55","tid":1755272,"uid":18959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:43:39.000Z","msg":"示威者先係沉默的大多數"},{"pid":"3b657df6adeb7f0dcc6809467ef0b9a07bd3acef","tid":1755272,"uid":58297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f815dda38bcc4d7a8ad82db1e92b27e5fc564477","tid":1755272,"uid":138609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:45:07.000Z","msg":"學毛澤東話齋<br />\n宜將剩勇追窮寇"},{"pid":"d11c1fd1e70acdb1af8712baf46d9da0ef22ab68","tid":1755272,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:46:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a81023a54e5d5eda0ac9515f4114fc2f5ac123c","tid":1755272,"uid":313216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:46:40.000Z","msg":"p push"},{"pid":"e385328b29797dcf8c9819600ee22f0762eab989","tid":1755272,"uid":201669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:46:45.000Z","msg":"正式宣佈1126黎明行動 三罷再開<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eAJkqS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eAJkqS</a><br />\n<br />\n點解冇成效呀<br />\n因為冇乜人行動，新聞又淡化炸<br />\n如果散水撚肯幫下手成件事就唔同啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ae96fa6d0729105db1aded2c30c82f16a1521d","tid":1755272,"uid":85327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e9d1890bc2bb3810b89b3c97e2e4343df27d850c","tid":1755272,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:49:46