:1755272,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090fb75f9761a85b1f1a6b2e4edeb10ea744e1ea","tid":1755272,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:01:09.000Z","msg":"雖然區選拎左389席<br />\n但咁嘅選舉制度下仲比建制狗拎到59席<br />\n只可以叫做小勝<br />\n大家開心完之後抗爭運動都要繼續落去<br />\nPOLY仲有一大班手足畀狗圍緊<br />\n仲有好多手足畀狗拉左畀人告緊<br />\n佢地等緊我地光復香港救佢地出黎<br />\n如果我地區選完就退<br />\n點對得住死左嘅手足<br />\n點對得住為我地擋子彈嘅手足<br />\n點對得住畀狗拉左嘅手足<br />\n所以18區要繼續開花<br />\n黎明行動要日日搞<br />\n組織全港大三罷<br />\n直到光復香港為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1754511/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1754511/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"6c8afa5ec3a676f9b97e859df22425a8ddd6e691","tid":1755272,"uid":158815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}